		<title>阿囉哈LED總匯點亮聖誕光影季　用專業打造最溫暖的節慶氛圍</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/20/%e9%98%bf%e5%9b%89%e5%93%88led%e7%b8%bd%e5%8c%af%e9%bb%9e%e4%ba%ae%e8%81%96%e8%aa%95%e5%85%89%e5%bd%b1%e5%ad%a3%e3%80%80%e7%94%a8%e5%b0%88%e6%a5%ad%e6%89%93%e9%80%a0%e6%9c%80%e6%ba%ab%e6%9a%96/</link>
		
