					<description><![CDATA[<p>▲從漁港到農村，梓官文化再生新風貌。（圖／記者莊全成攝） 記者 莊全成／高雄報導 高雄梓官融合漁村與農村風情， &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/19/%e6%a2%93%e5%ae%98%e8%b5%a4%e8%a5%bf%e6%bc%81%e6%9d%91%e5%b1%95%e6%96%b0%e9%a2%a8%e8%b2%8c-%e6%96%87%e5%8c%96%e5%86%8d%e7%94%9f%e7%b5%90%e5%90%88%e8%be%b2%e6%9d%91%e6%85%a2%e9%81%8a%e9%ab%94%e9%a9%97/">梓官赤西漁村展新風貌 文化再生結合農村慢遊體驗</a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="812" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625601_0-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C812&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-269592" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625601_0-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625601_0-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C511&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625601_0-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1023&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625601_0-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1364&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625601_0-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">▲從漁港到農村，梓官文化再生新風貌。（圖／記者莊全成攝）</figcaption></figure>



<p>記者 莊全成／高雄報導</p>



<p>高雄梓官融合漁村與農村風情，展現地方文化新樣貌。赤西社區於10月18日舉辦「赤西漁村生活美學體驗活動」，邀遊客走讀百年古厝、品嚐在地海鮮套餐、體驗搓魚丸樂趣，並由攝影達人帶領拍出漁村風情美照。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="813" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625599_0-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C813&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-269594" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625599_0-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625599_0-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625599_0-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625599_0-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1366&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625599_0-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">▲現場還有食農教育講座、農夫市集、文化展演、大地遊戲、料理秀、獨立書店、攝影成果等。（圖／記者莊全成攝）</figcaption></figure>



<p>赤西里長劉英凱推動文化導覽及線上QR-code導覽系統，讓旅客更深入了解社區故事。社區並結合高市農業局輔導，利用廢棄漁具創作裝置藝術《共生之門》，象徵人海共生與文化再生。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="814" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625600_0-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C814&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-269597" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625600_0-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625600_0-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625600_0-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1025&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625600_0-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1366&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/625600_0-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">▲讓遊客使用在地食材虱目魚漿親手體驗搓魚丸的樂趣，吹著海風品嚐現煮的魚丸湯。（圖／記者莊全成攝）</figcaption></figure>



<p>活動同步串聯「梓感農村文化節」，推出牛耕體驗、農夫市集、料理秀與攝影展等多元活動，串連漁村與農村，讓旅客體驗質感滿分的慢遊之旅。更多活動資訊可上臉書「梓官赤西 海岸日常」查詢。</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/19/%e6%a2%93%e5%ae%98%e8%b5%a4%e8%a5%bf%e6%bc%81%e6%9d%91%e5%b1%95%e6%96%b0%e9%a2%a8%e8%b2%8c-%e6%96%87%e5%8c%96%e5%86%8d%e7%94%9f%e7%b5%90%e5%90%88%e8%be%b2%e6%9d%91%e6%85%a2%e9%81%8a%e9%ab%94%e9%a9%97/">梓官赤西漁村展新風貌 文化再生結合農村慢遊體驗</a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
